data.description: This newly updated 4-bedroom,2-full-baths + Flex space from converted garage in the Martin High School district offers a fresh and modern living space. With its newly painted interior & exterior, updated hardware, stylish fans, modern new appliances, renovated bathrooms, new carpeting, new water heater, well-maintained lawn, new sod backyard, and new secure fence, this home is truly move-in ready. Buyer & Buyers Agent to verify all MLS information.
